attributes.title: Retrieve Error Logs
attributes.description: Logs with log.level == ERROR, sorted descending, keeping specific fields.

kibanaSavedObjectMeta.searchSourceJSON:
{"query": {"esql": "FROM unstructured-logs
| where log.level == "ERROR"
| sort @timestamp desc
| keep @timestamp, source, message"}, "index": {"id": "unstructured-logs", "title": "unstructured-logs", "timeFieldName": "@timestamp", "sourceFilters": [], "type": "esql", "fieldFormats": {}, "runtimeFieldMap": {}, "allowNoIndex": false, "name": "unstructured-logs", "allowHidden": false}, "filter": []}

attributes.title: Parse AuthService Logs with Dissect
attributes.description: Extracts user and IP address from AuthService logs using dissect.

kibanaSavedObjectMeta.searchSourceJSON:
{"query": {"esql": "FROM unstructured-logs
| dissect message "User '%{user}' logged in successfully from IP address %{ip_address}"
| where source == "AuthService" and log.level == "INFO"
| sort @timestamp desc
| keep @timestamp, user, ip_address"}, "index": {"id": "unstructured-logs", "title": "unstructured-logs", "timeFieldName": "@timestamp", "sourceFilters": [], "type": "esql", "fieldFormats": {}, "runtimeFieldMap": {}, "allowNoIndex": false, "name": "unstructured-logs", "allowHidden": false}, "filter": []}
